 &lt;li&gt;Spring Security lead &lt;em&gt;also&lt;/em&gt; blogged about &lt;a href=&quot;http://spring.io/blog/2014/05/23/preview-spring-security-test-web-security&quot;&gt;using Spring Security Test to handle web security&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
